      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "These schema definition files contain a codified version of the specification addendum defined by ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/usdz-schemas-for-ar",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". As a developer of third-party DCC software, you enable your users to configure interactive and AR features in their 3D assets by implementing the specification and providing additional UI.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Integrate-Interactive-and-AR-Schemas",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Integrate Interactive and AR Schemas",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To recognize and validate syntax, and to participate in USD features such as transform hierarchies, incorporate the new interactive and AR schemas into your DCC by copying the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "schema.usda",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " files into your USD library and rebuilding. For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://graphics.pixar.com/usd/docs/Generating-New-Schema-Classes.html",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
